#### 9. UsersPage/RolesPage: inline arrow onClick in map loops

**Files:** [UsersPage.tsx](frontend/src/pages/UsersPage.tsx#L137-L138), [RolesPage.tsx](frontend/src/pages/RolesPage.tsx#L109-L114)

**Issue:** `onClick={() => handleEdit(user)}` and `onClick={() => handleDelete(user)}` inside `.map()` create new functions per row per render.

**Fix:** Extract row components (`UserRow`, `RoleRow`) wrapped in `React.memo`, receiving stable `onEdit`/`onDelete` callbacks:
```tsx
// UsersPage
const handleEdit = useCallback((user: User) => { /* ... */ }, [roles]);
const handleDelete = useCallback(async (user: User) => { /* ... */ }, [showToast]);
```

